author: KEXP
description: Japanese experimental artist @harunemuri presents a unique set of poetic-punk fused with orchestral noise and fragmented pop on her latest release 'ekkolaptómenos'. Live on KEXP, she sends listeners to new sonic worlds with a performance of "anointment" and more across the album.
title: HARU NEMURI performs "anointment" and more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
